# CONFIGURATION NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# FIT RATES REFERENCE:
# - CPU: 80-150 FIT (typical for enterprise processors)
# - HDD: 800-1200 FIT (7200rpm enterprise drives) 
# - SSD: 50-300 FIT (enterprise vs consumer grade)
